  "keyFeatures": [
    "57 tools across 10 categories for complete iOS Simulator control",
    "Accessibility-first approach with structured snapshot API (like Playwright)",
    "Cursor-free touch injection via Facebook idb (IndigoHID)",
    "AI-optimized screenshots and video key-frame extraction",
    "Works with Claude Code, Cursor, Windsurf, VS Code, Zed, and any MCP client",
    "Full debugging suite: crash logs, live log streaming, file inspection",
    "Advanced testing: Dynamic Type, biometric auth, location simulation, UserDefaults"
  ],
